You can simply ask Alexa to control your Rojeco Smart products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “ROJECO” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in “ROJECO” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Rojeco Smart” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Rojeco Smart” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Rojeco Smart” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on pet feeder.
Alexa, turn off pet feeder.
Alexa, show me the pet camera.
